---
import Layout from "src/layouts/layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="The benefits" language="en">
  <div id="Block-1">
    <div class="h-screen w-screen overflow-hidden">
      <img
        id="TheBackGorundImage"
        class="h-auto w-screen Background object-cover origin-center"
        src="/img/background/71a47a13d15979bca920b43639251dde.jpeg"
        alt="Tea"
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="Block-2" class="mx-24">
    <p class="Headline-1">“Camellia sinensis”</p>
    <p class="Text w-[58rem]">
      Tea is the dried leaves of the Camellia sinensis plant, a small tree in
      the Theaceae family. White Tea, Green Tea and Black Tea such as many other
      Teas are all from the same plant.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div id="Block-3" class="flex flex-row mx-24">
    <p class="w-1/3 Text mt-8">
      This plant contains biochemical compounds called polyphenols, which
      include flavonoids. The latter are also found in fruits and vegetables and
      are antioxidants, which prevents the degeneration of cells, responsible
      for more than 50 diseases.
    </p>
    <img
      src="/img/background/ed02f3f0d6c5efd0779431978d6dc6b0.png"
      alt=""
      srcset=""
      class="w-1/3"
    />
    <p class="w-1/3 Text mt-auto mb-8">
      The nearly 3,000 tea varieties that exist all over the world differ in
      flavour and characteristics depending on the geographical area of
      ​​origin, atmospheric conditions, quality, and even the altitude at which
      it is produced.
    </p>

    <div class="absolute w-screen h-screen">
      <svg class="w-screen h-screen">
        <line
          x1="12%"
          y1="24%"
          x2="12%"
          y2="34%"
          stroke="black"
          stroke-width="2"></line>
        <line
          x1="12%"
          y1="34%"
          x2="30%"
          y2="34%"
          stroke="black"
          stroke-width="2"></line>

        <line
          x1="58%"
          y1="10%"
          x2="76%"
          y2="10%"
          stroke="black"
          stroke-width="2"></line>
        <line
          x1="76%"
          y1="10%"
          x2="76%"
          y2="28%"
          stroke="black"
          stroke-width="2"></line>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="Block-4" class="flex flex-row pb-12">
    <svg class="absolute w-screen h-screen">
      <line x1="50%" y1="0%" x2="50%" y2="34%" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"
      ></line>
      <line x1="50%" y1="34%" x2="8%" y2="34%" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"
      ></line>
      <line x1="8%" y1="34%" x2="8%" y2="50%" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"
      ></line>

      <line x1="8%" y1="58%" x2="8%" y2="70%" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"
      ></line>
      <line x1="8%" y1="78%" x2="8%" y2="90%" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"
      ></line>

      <line x1="50%" y1="34%" x2="84%" y2="34%" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"
      ></line>
      <line x1="84%" y1="34%" x2="84%" y2="38%" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"
      ></line>

      <line x1="84%" y1="46%" x2="84%" y2="50%" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"
      ></line>
      <line x1="84%" y1="50%" x2="96%" y2="50%" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"
      ></line>
      <line x1="96%" y1="55%" x2="96%" y2="50%" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"
      ></line>
      <line x1="96%" y1="63%" x2="96%" y2="66%" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"
